WORK_DESCR_LO:
Regarding the Grease, NOV have a few different original valve manufacturers now under their ownership and therefore had different recommended greases for each type.  They have tried to consolidate this by giving sending this PIB to standardise the properties we should look for in a general grease.  I have been recommending that we standardise on the WOM valve grease MS-0050 for high temp.  This will cover all applications and operating temps on all Rigs and is currently the most used.

Regarding the POCV and shuttle valves, it is an information bulletin regarding the correct repair kits we should use for each specific valve so we do not try to substitute with something that will restrict the full operation of any valve.
